I'm begging you for advice! Should I continue the search or is it a stupid idea? The only things I managed to get my hands on are rumours about a certain Gunsmith, a pair of worn-out boots, a 7,62х51 bullet to my left side and three tushkano teeth in my left ankle.
Honestly, I'm desperate. But if you insist on me continuing the search, then I ask for my reward to be doubled! I hope you agree with this.
Yes! And travel expenses too, it's time to toss me some money. If you agree with my conditions, I'm waiting for my payment in advance at the old place, in the attic of a house you certainly know.

